of cached values. If [%-*@3 maxsize] is zero, calls AdjustValueCache 
and any further calls to AdjustValueCache adjust it. If [%-*@3 maxsize] 
is greater than zero, limits are fixed to [%-*@3 maxsize][%-  and 
][%-*@3 maxcount].&]
